Darren (the creator of this application) did an excellent job on it!  1.) Obviously where we are all here for (the EQ in the background as wallpaper) is responsive when I raise and lower my volume (elongates or comes to a stop).  2.) There are different theme styles available to choose from if the user doesn't like the default rainbow theme, one can choose a different stock theme (Retro Geometric) at no additional cost or can try a different theme for 5 minutes ( Aurora or Strings) and decide whether they like them enough to purchase them.  3.) One can customize the details of the EQ (e.g. super reflective EQ bars, amount of particles on the screen, scalable EQ bars [if they are too short or too big].  4.) If one so desires, it can be animated in the background if there isn't any music playing.  I only have a single request for this app, which I think may be an unfair request when I think about it,  My single request: Have the application's visuals fill up the lock screen for Moto G5 Plus or Smartphones in general, that would be awesome!  Lastly, thank you for getting back to me on the email today, better late than never!  Best,  Miguel P.
